text.div:
Diet

This value set defines a set of codes that can be used to indicate the encounter priority as determined by triage.

This value set defines it's own terms in the system http://hl7.org/fhir/diet

CodeDisplayDefinition
immImmediateWithin seconds
emgEmergencyWithin 10 minutes
urgUrgentWithin 30 minutes
s-urgSemi-urgentWithin 60 minutes
no-urgNon-urgentWithin 120 minutes
